<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Doughborough — Pizza &amp; Bread Dough Calculator with Real Fermentation Timing</title>
<meta name="description" content="Free pizza and bread dough calculator that adjusts yeast and fermentation time to your kitchen temperature. Eight styles, cold-ferment planning, and plain-language guides.">
<meta property="og:title" content="Doughborough — Pizza &amp; Bread Dough Calculator">
<meta property="og:description" content="Dough weights and fermentation timing tuned to your kitchen. Eight styles, cold-ferment planning, honest ranges instead of false precision.">
<meta property="og:type" content="website">
<meta property="og:site_name" content="Doughborough">
<meta property="og:url" content="https://doughborough.com/">
<meta property="og:image" content="https://doughborough.com/og-image.png">
<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
<meta name="twitter:title" content="Doughborough — Pizza &amp; Bread Dough Calculator">
<meta name="twitter:description" content="Dough weights and fermentation timing tuned to your kitchen.">
<meta name="twitter:image" content="https://doughborough.com/og-image.png">
<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
<link rel="canonical" href="https://doughborough.com/">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,400;0,9..144,500;0,9..144,600;0,9..144,700;0,9..144,900;1,9..144,500&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "SoftwareApplication",
  "name": "Doughborough",
  "applicationCategory": "LifestyleApplication",
  "description": "Pizza and bread dough calculator with fermentation timing that adjusts to kitchen temperature.",
  "operatingSystem": "Web",
  "offers": { "@type": "Offer", "price": "0" }
}
</script>
<style>
  :root{
    --char:#1C1815;        /* deep warm charcoal base */
    --char-2:#26211C;      /* raised charcoal */
    --char-3:#322B24;      /* card charcoal */
    --proof:#F2C14E;       /* proof-yellow, the rise moment */
    --proof-soft:#E8B94A;
    --blush:#C4633F;       /* fermentation terracotta — accent only */
    --cream:#F5F0E6;       /* warm off-white surface */
    --cream-dim:#D9D2C4;
    --crust:#8A6D52;       /* muted crust brown */
    --crust-soft:#A88B6E;
    --line:rgba(245,240,230,0.10);
    --line-2:rgba(245,240,230,0.18);
    --shadow:0 24px 60px -20px rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
    --maxw:1180px;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
  body{
    background:var(--char);
    color:var(--cream);
    font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;
    line-height:1.6;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
    overflow-x:hidden;
    width:100%;
  }
  img,svg{max-width:100%}
  ::selection{background:var(--proof);color:var(--char)}
  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}
  .wrap{max-width:var(--maxw);margin:0 auto;padding:0 28px}

  /* ---- type scale ---- */
  .display{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:600;line-height:1.0;letter-spacing:-0.02em}
  .mono{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace}
  .eyebrow{
    font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.22em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--crust-soft);
  }

  /* ---- nav ---- */
  nav{
    position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;
    background:rgba(28,24,21,0.82);backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .nav-inner{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:70px}
  .brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px;font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:600;font-size:22px;letter-spacing:-0.01em}
  .brand .mark{
    width:30px;height:30px;flex:none;border-radius:50%;
    background:radial-gradient(circle at 34% 30%, var(--proof), var(--blush) 78%);
    box-shadow:0 0 0 1px rgba(242,193,78,0.35), inset 0 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
  }
  .nav-links{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:30px;font-size:15px}
  .nav-links a{color:var(--cream-dim);transition:color .18s}
  .nav-links a:hover{color:var(--cream)}
  .nav-cta{
    background:var(--proof);color:var(--char);font-weight:600;
    padding:9px 18px;border-radius:8px;font-size:14px;transition:transform .16s, box-shadow .16s;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover{transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 8px 22px -8px rgba(242,193,78,0.6)}
  .nav-links .link-plain{display:none}
  @media(min-width:820px){.nav-links .link-plain{display:inline}}

  /* ---- hero ---- */
  .hero{position:relative;padding:74px 0 40px;overflow:hidden}
  .hero-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:44px;align-items:center}
  @media(min-width:960px){.hero-grid{grid-template-columns:1.05fr 0.95fr;gap:56px}}
  .hero h1{
    font-size:clamp(44px,7vw,80px);margin:18px 0 22px;
  }
  .hero h1 .warm{color:var(--proof);font-style:italic;font-weight:500}
  .lede{font-size:clamp(17px,2.1vw,20px);color:var(--cream-dim);max-width:30em;margin-bottom:30px}
  .hero-cta-row{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:14px;align-items:center}
  .btn-primary{
    background:var(--proof);color:var(--char);font-weight:600;font-size:16px;
    padding:15px 28px;border-radius:11px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
    transition:transform .16s, box-shadow .16s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 14px 34px -12px rgba(242,193,78,0.65)}
  .btn-primary svg{transition:transform .2s}
  .btn-primary:hover svg{transform:translateX(3px)}
  .btn-ghost{
    color:var(--cream);font-weight:500;font-size:16px;padding:15px 20px;
    border:1px solid var(--line-2);border-radius:11px;transition:background .18s,border-color .18s;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover{background:var(--char-3);border-color:var(--crust)}

  .hero-tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin-top:26px}
  .tag{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;color:var(--crust-soft);
    border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:20px;padding:5px 12px}

  /* ---- fermentation instrument (signature) ---- */
  .instrument{
    background:linear-gradient(160deg,var(--char-2),var(--char-3));
    border:1px solid var(--line-2);border-radius:18px;padding:24px 24px 20px;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow);position:relative;
  }
  .inst-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:6px}
  .inst-title{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--crust-soft)}
  .inst-read{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--proof)}
  .curve-wrap{position:relative;width:100%}
  svg.curve{width:100%;height:auto;display:block;touch-action:none;cursor:ew-resize}
  .inst-foot{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-top:14px;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  @media(max-width:420px){.inst-hint{text-align:left;max-width:100%}}
  .inst-metric{text-align:left}
  .inst-metric .k{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--crust-soft)}
  .inst-metric .v{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,34px);font-weight:600;line-height:1.05;color:var(--cream)}
  .inst-metric .v .u{font-size:15px;color:var(--cream-dim);font-weight:500}
  .inst-hint{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--crust-soft);text-align:right;max-width:15em}
  .slider-row{margin-top:16px}
  .slider-row label{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--crust-soft);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:8px}
  input[type=range]{-webkit-appearance:none;appearance:none;width:100%;height:5px;border-radius:5px;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--blush),var(--proof));outline:none}
  input[type=range]::-webkit-slider-thumb{-webkit-appearance:none;appearance:none;width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--cream);border:3px solid var(--proof);cursor:ew-resize;box-shadow:0 3px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);transition:transform .1s}
  input[type=range]::-webkit-slider-thumb:hover{transform:scale(1.12)}
  input[type=range]::-moz-range-thumb{width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--cream);border:3px solid var(--proof);cursor:ew-resize}

  /* ---- section frame ---- */
  section.block{padding:76px 0}
  .sec-head{max-width:40em;margin-bottom:44px}
  .sec-head h2{font-size:clamp(30px,4.4vw,46px);margin:14px 0 16px}
  .sec-head p{color:var(--cream-dim);font-size:17px}

  /* ---- how it thinks: three principles ---- */
  .principles{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:1px;background:var(--line);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden}
  @media(min-width:760px){.principles{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}}
  .principle{background:var(--char-2);padding:32px 28px;transition:background .2s}
  .principle:hover{background:var(--char-3)}
  .principle .n{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;color:var(--blush);letter-spacing:0.1em}
  .principle h3{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:600;font-size:22px;margin:14px 0 10px;line-height:1.15}
  .principle p{color:var(--cream-dim);font-size:15px}

  /* ---- guides ---- */
  .guides-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:20px}
  @media(min-width:680px){.guides-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}
  @media(min-width:1000px){.guides-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr}}
  .guide{
    background:var(--char-2);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;
    padding:26px 24px 22px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;
    transition:transform .18s, border-color .18s, background .18s;cursor:pointer;position:relative;
    color:inherit;text-decoration:none;
  }
  .guide:hover{transform:translateY(-4px);border-color:var(--crust);background:var(--char-3)}
  .guide .q{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--crust-soft)}
  .guide h3{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:600;font-size:21px;line-height:1.2}
  .guide .snippet{color:var(--cream-dim);font-size:14.5px;flex:1}
  .guide .read{font-size:13px;color:var(--proof);font-weight:500;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-top:4px}
  .guide .read svg{transition:transform .2s}
  .guide:hover .read svg{transform:translateX(3px)}

  /* ---- article reader (expandable) ---- */
  .reader-backdrop{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(10,8,6,0.72);backdrop-filter:blur(6px);z-index:100;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity .28s}
  .reader-backdrop.open{opacity:1;pointer-events:auto}
  .reader{
    position:fixed;top:0;right:0;height:100%;width:min(660px,100%);z-index:101;
    background:var(--cream);color:var(--char);transform:translateX(100%);transition:transform .34s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.15,1);
    overflow-y:auto;box-shadow:-30px 0 80px -20px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
  }
  .reader.open{transform:translateX(0)}
  .reader-inner{padding:56px clamp(28px,5vw,60px) 80px}
  .reader-close{position:sticky;top:20px;float:right;margin-left:16px;width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;border:1px solid rgba(28,24,21,0.18);background:var(--cream);color:var(--char);font-size:20px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:background .16s}
  .reader-close:hover{background:#EBE4D6}
  .reader .a-eyebrow{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--blush);margin-bottom:14px}
  .reader h1{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:600;font-size:clamp(30px,5vw,42px);line-height:1.08;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:8px}
  .reader .a-answer{font-size:19px;line-height:1.55;color:#2C2620;background:#EDE6D8;border-left:3px solid var(--proof);padding:18px 22px;border-radius:0 10px 10px 0;margin:24px 0 30px;font-weight:500}
  .reader h2{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:600;font-size:26px;margin:34px 0 12px;line-height:1.2}
  .reader p{font-size:16.5px;line-height:1.72;color:#3A332B;margin-bottom:16px}
  .reader ul{margin:0 0 18px 20px}
  .reader li{font-size:16.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#3A332B;margin-bottom:8px}
  .reader strong{color:var(--char);font-weight:600}
  .reader .a-cta{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;background:var(--char);color:var(--cream);font-weight:600;padding:15px 26px;border-radius:11px;margin-top:20px;transition:transform .16s,box-shadow .16s;font-size:15.5px}
  .reader .a-cta:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 12px 28px -10px rgba(28,24,21,0.5)}
  .reader .a-cta svg{transition:transform .2s}
  .reader .a-cta:hover svg{transform:translateX(3px)}
  .reader .a-meta{font-size:13px;color:#8A7D68;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;margin-top:40px;padding-top:20px;border-top:1px solid rgba(28,24,21,0.12)}

  /* ---- styles strip ---- */
  .styles-strip{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;margin-top:8px}
  .style-chip{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:16px;color:var(--cream);border:1px solid var(--line-2);border-radius:30px;padding:8px 18px;background:var(--char-2);transition:background .18s,color .18s}
  .style-chip:hover{background:var(--proof);color:var(--char)}

  /* ---- big CTA band ---- */
  .cta-band{background:linear-gradient(155deg,var(--blush),#9E4C2E);border-radius:22px;padding:clamp(40px,6vw,72px);text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
  .cta-band::after{content:"";position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(circle at 78% 18%, rgba(242,193,78,0.28), transparent 55%);pointer-events:none}
  .cta-band h2{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:600;font-size:clamp(30px,5vw,50px);line-height:1.05;margin-bottom:18px;position:relative}
  .cta-band p{color:rgba(245,240,230,0.9);font-size:18px;max-width:34em;margin:0 auto 30px;position:relative}
  .cta-band .btn-primary{position:relative}

  /* ---- footer ---- */
  footer{border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding:52px 0 40px;margin-top:20px}
  .foot-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:32px}
  @media(min-width:720px){.foot-grid{grid-template-columns:1.4fr 1fr 1fr}}
  .foot-brand p{color:var(--crust-soft);font-size:14px;max-width:24em;margin-top:14px}
  .foot-col h4{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--crust-soft);margin-bottom:16px}
  .foot-col a{display:block;color:var(--cream-dim);font-size:14.5px;margin-bottom:10px;transition:color .16s}
  .foot-col a:hover{color:var(--proof)}
  .foot-legal{margin-top:44px;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--crust-soft);font-size:13px;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px}

  @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){*{transition:none!important;scroll-behavior:auto!important}}
  :focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--proof);outline-offset:3px;border-radius:4px}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="wrap nav-inner">
    <a href="#top" class="brand"><span class="mark"></span>Doughborough</a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#how" class="link-plain">How it works</a>
      <a href="#guides" class="link-plain">Guides</a>
      <a href="#styles" class="link-plain">Styles</a>
      <a href="/calculator.html" class="nav-cta">Open calculator</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<a id="top"></a>
<header class="hero">
  <div class="wrap hero-grid">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <span class="eyebrow">Pizza &amp; bread dough calculator</span>
      <h1 class="display">The dough maths,<br><span class="warm">tuned to your kitchen.</span></h1>
      <p class="lede">Most calculators hand you a recipe and hope your room is 25&nbsp;°C. Doughborough scales the flour and water to what you're making, then adjusts the yeast and fermentation plan to the temperature you're actually working in — for eight pizza and bread styles, warm or cold-fermented.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta-row">
        <a href="/calculator.html" class="btn-primary">Open the calculator
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="#how" class="btn-ghost">See how it thinks</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-tags">
        <span class="tag">8 styles</span>
        <span class="tag">Cold-ferment planning</span>
        <span class="tag">Poolish &amp; biga</span>
        <span class="tag">Honest time ranges</span>
        <span class="tag">Free · no sign-up</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SIGNATURE: live fermentation instrument -->
    <div class="instrument" id="instrument">
      <div class="inst-head">
        <span class="inst-title">Room-temperature reference</span>
        <span class="inst-read" id="instRead">25 °C</span>
      </div>
      <div class="curve-wrap">
        <svg class="curve" id="curve" viewBox="0 0 460 240" role="img" aria-label="Fermentation speed against temperature">
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="fill" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
              <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#F2C14E" stop-opacity="0.34"/>
              <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#F2C14E" stop-opacity="0"/>
            </linearGradient>
          </defs>
          <!-- gridlines -->
          <g stroke="rgba(245,240,230,0.08)" stroke-width="1">
            <line x1="40" y1="30" x2="40" y2="200"/>
            <line x1="40" y1="200" x2="440" y2="200"/>
          </g>
          <path id="area" fill="url(#fill)"></path>
          <path id="line" fill="none" stroke="#F2C14E" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
          <line id="marker" stroke="#C4633F" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="4 4"></line>
          <circle id="dot" r="6" fill="#F5F0E6" stroke="#C4633F" stroke-width="3"></circle>
          <!-- axis labels -->
          <text x="40" y="222" fill="#A88B6E" font-family="IBM Plex Mono" font-size="11">10°C</text>
          <text x="240" y="222" fill="#A88B6E" font-family="IBM Plex Mono" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle">22°C</text>
          <text x="440" y="222" fill="#A88B6E" font-family="IBM Plex Mono" font-size="11" text-anchor="end">35°C</text>
          <text x="34" y="36" fill="#A88B6E" font-family="IBM Plex Mono" font-size="11" text-anchor="end">fast</text>
          <text x="34" y="200" fill="#A88B6E" font-family="IBM Plex Mono" font-size="11" text-anchor="end">slow</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="slider-row">
        <label><span>Kitchen temperature</span><span id="tempLabel" class="mono">25 °C</span></label>
        <input type="range" id="temp" min="10" max="35" value="25" step="1" aria-label="Kitchen temperature">
      </div>
      <div class="inst-foot">
        <div class="inst-metric">
          <div class="k">Est. bulk + proof</div>
          <div class="v" id="timeOut">8<span class="u"> h</span></div>
        </div>
        <p class="inst-hint" id="instHint">Drag the temperature. Warmer ferments faster; the calculator adjusts the timing and yeast dose around it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- HOW IT THINKS -->
<section class="block" id="how">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Why it's different</span>
      <h2 class="display">A calculator that respects the science, then hides it.</h2>
      <p>Dough is a slow chemical reaction. Three ideas separate Doughborough from a recipe printed on a card — and none of them ask you to understand fermentation to get a loaf out of it.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="principles">
      <div class="principle">
        <span class="n">01</span>
        <h3>Temperature drives everything</h3>
        <p>Within normal room temperatures, fermentation accelerates sharply as the kitchen gets warmer — a recipe that's perfect at 25&nbsp;°C is over-proved at 30 and asleep at 15. Doughborough scales the timing and yeast dose to the room you're actually in. Refrigerator fermentation behaves differently, so it's modelled separately.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="principle">
        <span class="n">02</span>
        <h3>Cold ferment is its own model</h3>
        <p>A fridge dough doesn't cool instantly. The first few hours ferment fast, then slow as the centre chills. Most tools ignore this; Doughborough integrates the cooling curve so an overnight plan is honest, not a guess.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="principle">
        <span class="n">03</span>
        <h3>Ranges, not false precision</h3>
        <p>No calculator can tell you dough is ready at exactly 7:45. So it won't pretend to. You get a time window and a thing to look for — puffy, jiggly, nearly doubled — because your eyes finish what the maths starts.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- GUIDES -->
<section class="block" id="guides" style="padding-top:20px">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Guides · straight answers</span>
      <h2 class="display">The questions every dough-maker Googles.</h2>
      <p>Short, practical answers to the things that actually go wrong — each guide links to the calculator with the relevant settings ready.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="guides-grid" id="guidesGrid"><!-- injected --></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STYLES -->
<section class="block" id="styles" style="padding-top:20px">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">One tool, eight doughs</span>
      <h2 class="display">From a blistered Neapolitan to a soft sandwich loaf.</h2>
      <p>Each style carries its own hydration, structure and bake behaviour. Pick one and the calculator changes its whole plan to match.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="styles-strip">
      <a href="/calculator.html?style=neapolitan" class="style-chip">Neapolitan</a>
      <a href="/calculator.html?style=ny" class="style-chip">New York</a>
      <a href="/calculator.html?style=detroit" class="style-chip">Detroit</a>
      <a href="/calculator.html?style=roman" class="style-chip">Roman al taglio</a>
      <a href="/calculator.html?style=focaccia" class="style-chip">Focaccia</a>
      <a href="/calculator.html?style=ciabatta" class="style-chip">Ciabatta</a>
      <a href="/calculator.html?style=baguette" class="style-chip">Baguette</a>
      <a href="/calculator.html?style=softbread" class="style-chip">Soft white bread</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA BAND -->
<section class="block" style="padding-top:20px">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="cta-band">
      <h2 class="display">Your kitchen. Your flour. The right numbers.</h2>
      <p>Tell it the style and your temperature. Get weights, a timing window, and a plan you can actually follow — free, in your browser, no account.</p>
      <a href="/calculator.html" class="btn-primary">Start with the calculator
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="foot-grid">
      <div class="foot-brand">
        <a href="#top" class="brand"><span class="mark"></span>Doughborough</a>
        <p>A dough calculator that treats fermentation like the temperature-dependent reaction it is — for home bakers who want the loaf, not a chemistry degree.</p>
